@DATABASE "Ikari Warriors"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - I - Ikari Warriors"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - I
                   ====================================

                              Ikari Warriors
                              ==============


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives   " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(39273,0)"}       39273,0
@{"Infinite Fuel    " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(40618,0)"}       40618,0
@{"Infinite Ammo    " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(39917,167)"}       39917,167
@{"Infinite Grenades" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(40076,167)"}       40076,167
@{"Tanks            " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(62384,190)"}       62384,190
@{"Immunity         " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(40272,0)"}       40272,0
@{"Lives = x        " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(41178,255)"}       41178,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         I have no idea what the "Tanks" POKE does, but I left
                         it in just in case...

                         The Immunity POKE makes you completely invincible,
                         and anything that touches you will die. The drawback
                         is that the game seems to keep pulling you forward
                         which makes it hard to shoot accurately, or get in
                         your tank. (It also makes the game COMPLETELY pointless)

                                                                      Rastan.
@endnode
